                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-43-off197 t17900526-43-cd198"></join>, one hundred and twenty copper halfpence, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17900526-43-victim445" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
